      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Period and culture that flourished in India ca. 1500 BCE-ca. 500 BCE, developing due to an influx of nomadic and pastoral peoples who spoke Indo-European languages and followed the early religion of Vedism. </Note_Text>
